---
import "@fontsource/dm-sans/500.css";
import "@fontsource/dm-serif-display";
import me from "@images/me.webp";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<Layout title="Nimo Beeren">
  <main class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto py-24 text-neutral-700">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end gap-16 mx-auto max-w-[1056px]">
      <div class="border-b-sky-300 border-b-4 whitespace-nowrap">
        <h1
          class="text-8xl font-serif font-normal text-neutral-800 inline-block"
        >
          Nimo<br />Beeren
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl ml-8 leading-none inline-block" aria-label="pronouns">
          he/him
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img
          src={me}
          class="rounded-full drop-shadow-[0_0_128px_theme(colors.sky.300)]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <header
      class="flex flex-col gap-4 mx-auto max-w-[624px] text-3xl leading-normal mt-32"
    >
      <p>Hi there! üëã</p>
      <p>
        I'm a software engineer based in Eindhoven. I build tools that help
        people use data, code and science to create great things.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mt-40 flex flex-col items-center mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-6xl font-normal text-neutral-800">Projects</h2>
      <div class="flex gap-12 mt-24 max-w-full flex-wrap justify-center">
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
        <div class="bg-sky-100 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0 w-80 h-[544px]"></div>
      </div>
      <a
        class="text-3xl text-sky-700 leading-none mt-16 flex gap-2 items-center justify-center"
        href="/projects"
        ><div>See more</div>
        <Icon pack="heroicons-solid" name="arrow-right" size={30} />
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-40 flex flex-col items-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-6xl font-normal text-neutral-800">About me</h2>
      <div class="text-3xl mt-24 leading-normal flex flex-col gap-4">
        <p>
          During my master's on computer science & engineering at TU/e I learned
          to do independent research, becoming fluent in the academic language.
          This skill was very valuable to me, because it gave me access to the
          cutting edge of technology. I could apply it in new ways, and create
          things nobody had tried before.
        </p>
        <p class="line-clamp-3">
          In the final year of my studies, I found a compelling subject in graph
          databases. I like how they let you structure your data in any way you
          like, free from technical distractions. But if we want to have good
          reliability, usability and peformance, it can be incredibly useful to
          set some limits on this structure. But it turned out that this was not
          very well supported, even at a theoretical level. So I decided to
          write a thesis about it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        class="text-3xl text-sky-700 leading-none mt-16 flex gap-2 items-center justify-center"
        href="/about"
        ><div>Read more</div>
        <Icon pack="heroicons-solid" name="arrow-right" size={30} />
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="flex justify-center mt-40">
      <div
        class="flex gap-12 items-center mx-auto py-8 px-12 bg-sky-100 border-b-4 border-b-sky-300"
      >
        <img src={me} width="192" class="rounded-full" />
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-center">
          <p class="text-3xl text-sky-700">I'm looking for new challenges!</p>
          <a
            class="text-2xl text-white bg-sky-600 px-12 py-5 rounded-3xl flex gap-4 items-center leading-none"
            href="mailto:nimobeern@gmail.com"
            >Send me an email<span
              aria-label="envelope"
              class="text-3xl leading-none">‚úâÔ∏è</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
